So you're confident in the premium service then in the back half of the year and then into '22, but it's just a question mark and just how quickly it's going to come back.

Kenny Rocker -- Executive Vice President of Marketing and Sales

I am. That's a good way to say it, Jason. I feel confident about the demand on the international Intermodal side.

Jason Seidl -- Cowen -- Analyst

Okay. I appreciate the time. As always thank you.

Kenny Rocker -- Executive Vice President of Marketing and Sales

Jason, Thank you.

Operator

There are no additional questions at this time. I will now turn the floor to Mr. Lance Fritz for closing comments.

Lance M. Fritz -- Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer

Thank you, Rob, and thank you all for your questions. Just a reminder, we have an upcoming virtual Investor Day on May four at 2:00 p.m. Eastern time. We're all looking forward to discussing our strategy and vision for Union Pacific, and we hope you're going to be able to attend with us. I wish you all good health, and take care.

Operator

[Operator Closing Remarks]

